INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('67', 'zh_cn', '借势ASE Eptonic建立全球数字营销矩阵', '  2016-08-04 | 美国 · 纽约', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_21_1473836133.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Affiliate Summit East 2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">已经落下帷幕，作为业内最受瞩目的行业峰会之一，背靠其十多年来在移动广告及网盟领域的强大网络，参会者群体的背后蕴藏着数百亿美元的营销商机。植根于中国，服务于全球的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">受邀出席本次大会，为期三天的大会中，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">切身感受到了最新的行业科技和趋势，纽约之行圆满结束。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>优质平台汇聚世界流量</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大会期间，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">展台迎来了众多的网盟和商务人士，在与到访者的交流中我们得知：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMN(Eptonic Media Network)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">平台海量的优质</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">offer</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、高效的资金结算、良好的业界口碑以及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">AM</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一对一的专属服务，都是吸引他们前来洽谈的重要因素。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic EMN</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">平台作为全球领先的渠道分发管理平台，掌握上千个独家热门</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">offer</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，覆盖全球热门行业，汇集全球优秀广告主。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMN</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">平台可以为渠道方提供结果分析与建议，提高转化率。依托于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的资金优势，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMN</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">平台在结算周期上也拥有明显的优势。不仅如此，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMN</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">平台还可以帮助渠道方加深对广告主的了解，并通过有效措施规避可预测的非理想营销方式。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>多点突破建立全球矩阵</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在过去的三年中，互联网广告在全球主要市场中的占比一直呈现上涨趋势。据预测，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年互联网将成为全球</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大主要市场中最大的广告媒介，而这</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大广告市场占据了全球广告支出的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28%</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。互联网正快速成长为最主流的广告平台，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为全球互联网广告行业中的佼佼者，面对互联网广告的爆炸性发展以及客户更加强烈的全球化意愿，将从全球市场的高度出发，在产品、技术、数据分析及服务等方面不断创新，建立一个更高效更专业的数字营销矩阵，为渠道商和广告主提供更完善服务的同时，从多点突破带给行业更多惊喜。</span></p>', null, '2', 'Affiliate Summit East 2016已经落下帷幕，Eptonic纽约之行完满收官！', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('76', 'en_us', 'Meeting us in Guangzhou Salon', '    2016-09-27 | Guangzhou, China', null, '<div id=\"img-content\" class=\"rich_media_area_primary\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px 15px; position: relative; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1;\"><h2 class=\"rich_media_title\" id=\"activity-name\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4;\"><p style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474375550.jpg\" style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; width: 994px;\"><br></p><p><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><br></span></font></p><p>On September 27th, 2016, the salon of overseas promotion of apps and mobile games was successfully held in Guangzhou. This salon gathered many specialists in the field of mobile internet and altogether ,there were five top leaders shared their special insights for overseas promotion. The following were the main point:</p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 24px; color: inherit;\"><br></span></p><p><img src=\"upload/article/45_1475226405.jpg\" style=\"width: 994px;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: inherit; font-family: Arial; font-size: 24px;\">Firstly, the mobile games market would keep on developing in the future and according to data, mobile games revenue accounted for 85% in the global mobile application store. For the overseas markets, Vietnam, Thailand, Egypt and Argentina would still be the popular markets. And, Mexico, Indonesia and Turkey would be the next emerging markets.</span><br></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: Arial; color: inherit;\">Secondly, the product preferences, payment habit, product characteristics were different in different countries, so while promoting overseas, all of these factors shall be taken into consideration.</span><br></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: Arial; color: inherit;\">Thirdly, to acquire Google\'s recommendation, we shall know what kinds of products were acquired by Google Play and try to avoid some competitive similar products and also know the application process for the promotion.</span><br></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: Arial; color: inherit;\">Fourth, while promoting, people might suffer from the problem of poor exposure volume and click rate, and high single click charge. In order to minimize these problems, all of the related factors of daily budget, click rate, correlation, update frequency, historical performance, platform features, material originality, and audience orientation shall be taken into consideration.</span><br></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: Arial; color: inherit;\">Lastly, always keep in touch with users to make the products acceptable and be needed by users.</span><br></p></h2></div>', null, '1', 'It is excited to announce that our salon held on September 27th, 2016 is around the corner.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('76', 'zh_cn', '问道公开课，听行业大咖分享推广运营经验', '    2016-09-27 | 中国 · 广州', null, '<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; widows: 1;\">2016年以来，随着移动游戏市场“寡头化”趋势越来越严重，整个行业正在陷入资本寒冬。中小游戏开发者生存和发展都面临更多更艰难的挑战，可谓举步维艰。随着国内市场的不景气，越来越多的厂商开始选择国外市场做发展，将自己的产品向推向全球市场成为了今年大家追逐的概念。</span><br></p><div class=\"rich_media_content \" id=\"js_content\" style=\"widows: 1; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; min-height: 350px;\"><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474375550.jpg\" style=\"width: 994px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么，如何让这些概念成为实实在在的助力，让广大厂商可以更为了解和熟知国际市场借此在寒冬中破冰？</span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">Eptonic</span>携手<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">游戏茶馆，共同</span>举办<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">问道公开课</span>「手游&amp;应用全球化运营推广之道」主题沙龙会议！</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">多位专精海外手游市场大佬为您解惑！</span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">9月27日，Eptonic与游戏茶馆联合举办的主题沙龙「问道公开课•手游&amp;应用全球化运营推广之道」在广州羊城创意园创新谷咖啡举行。这次活动邀请了数位总监级别以上的参会者，他们畅聊手游，并分享自己关于移动应用出海的见解。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 class=\"rich_media_title\" id=\"activity-name\" style=\"line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;\"><p><img src=\"upload/article/45_1475226405.jpg\" style=\"width: 994px;\"></p></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><b>全球市场目前是个什么状况</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在主题沙龙的开场，Eptonic华南区商务负责人张姝带来了详细的全球市场概况分享。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">未来全球移动应用商店的收入还会再上一个台阶，达到千亿美元的级别，而手游占据全部收入的85%，可见未来的全球手游市场仍然有可观的收入空间。在海外市场中，越南、泰国、埃及和阿根廷处在应用发展的前沿，潜力较大；而下一轮增长浪潮将会出现在墨西哥、印尼和土耳其这三个国家。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">张姝还介绍了全球各个地区不同的产品偏好，并详细分析了这些国家和地区的市场。产品出海需要从五个维度去考虑策略，分别是：产品本身是否具有高质量？产品的格局考虑是什么？产品的本地化能做到什么程度？能否适应不同的支付习惯和渠道？产品的运营能力如何？</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><b><br></b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><b>如何获得Google Play与App Store的推荐</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">产品走向海外市场的过程中，获得两大应用商店的推荐无疑是最佳助力。Efun国际渠道负责人沈忱和谷得游戏联合创始人罗维分别带来了获得Google Play和App Store推荐的经验。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">首先当然是要了解这两大应用商店对于推荐产品的要求。比如Google Play，在同期竞争产品中具有独特性的更受青睐，同时产品APK要符合它的基本要求及政策条款。因此，推广前了解Google Play未来1~2个月游戏走向，游戏上线时期尽量避开太多同类产品竞争压力。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">其次是了解两大应用商店申请推广的流程，详细到推广申请书要如何写，展示PPT要怎么突出产品特点等，这些都能增加申请成功率。如Google Play，游戏上线前一个月为提交申请最佳时间；而App Store除了提前联系之外，产品上线后还需要提前三周确定更新日期。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><b><br></b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><b>全球化推广和运营的经验</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Eptonic 全球流量拓展部负责人吕晓波从展现量、点击率、单次点击费用三个方面谈推广过程中可能遇到的问题，并分析了影响这三个指标的因素。以展现量来说，日预算、点击率、相关度、更新频率和历史表现都会影响到展现量。其中，点击率是直接影响展现量的和新数据。而点击率又受到平台特性、文案/素材创意、受众定向的影响。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">卓盟乐变科技CEO黄杲则谈了精细化运营的问题，提出APP热更新的概念：即采用差分算法，通过集成很小的SDK实现手游版本更新，80%以上的用户在WiFi环境下无感知、无安装、自动完成升级过程，为用户节省流量、为App和游戏降低流失。<br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><b>新时代的龟速成功：始终保持对用户的了解</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">天梯互娱总经理钟虹以「龟兔赛跑」来比喻新时代的产品成功。钟虹分享了天梯互娱用8年时间研发一款产品，并在下一个8年保持这款产品生命力的故事。这其中最重要的一点，就是始终保持对用户的了解，以使自己的产品能够与时俱进地满足用户的需求。要实现这一点，持续性的用户调研，和线下与用户沟通的活动都是必不可少的。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在这次主题沙龙活动中，上述几位的分享为在迷茫中的中小开发者梳理与分享移动出海的机会点与实战经验。开发者和创业者在收获干货的同时，也进行了面对面交流和头脑风暴。<br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我们相信，在进军海外市场的过程中，这样的交流活动会助力更多企业从容布局海外。</p><div style=\"font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br></div></div>', null, '2', '9月27日，Eptonic与游戏茶馆联合主办问道沙龙，邀您来参加。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('67', 'en_us', 'Affiliate Summit East 2016 ', '  2016-08-04 | New York, USA', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 18.5714px;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_21_1473836133.jpg\" style=\"width: 1548px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\" lang=\"EN-US\">Affiliate Summit East 2016\nwas held in New York from July 31<sup>st</sup> to August 2<sup>nd</sup>,\nattracting thousands of affiliates and business people. As the global leader in\nmobile integrated marketing, Eptonic was invited to attend this conference.\nAiming to share industry experience and future trends of digital marketing with\nothers, and promoting the cooperation, Eptonic sent out the most professional\nteam.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', null, '1', 'It is really a great conference for everyone. Eptonic made itself known by many people with its professional advertising service.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('83', 'en_us', '「Keep Forward Hand by Hand」', '  2016-04-08 | Chongqing, China', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474527498.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">On April 8, 2016, the salon, “Keep\nForward Hand by Hand” was held in Chongqing, gathering many developers from\nChengdu, Shanghai, and Chongqing. As the leading platform of overseas promotion\nfor apps and mobile games, Eptonic was invited to attend this salon.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">With great challenges for developing in\ndomestic country, more and more enterprises are finding a way out to the global\nmarkets. Many developers had showed great interest in promotion overseas, but\nmeanwhile, they had concerns about the strange foreign markets.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic shared the latest information and\nanalysis about overseas markets and offered its creative promotion scheme,\nencouraging developers a lot.<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>', null, '1', 'On April 8th, 2016, the salon, “Keep Forward Hand by Hand” was held in Chongqing, gathering many developers from Chengdu, Shanghai, and Chongqing. ', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('72', 'zh_cn', '亮相iWorld移动游戏论坛，Eptonic陪你「游走世界」', '       ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474274306.jpg\" style=\"width: 50%;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">iWorld2016</span><span style=\"font-family:\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">数字世界博览会于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日在成都世纪城新国际会展中心盛大开幕。本次盛会由国际数据集团（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IDG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">）主办，是全球最大的聚焦移动互联生态圈相关产品和运用的展览和会议活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">来自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IDG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">及国内外互联网领域的企业高层和行业代表齐聚成都，以国际化视角，对移动互联生态圈的全球创新趋势进行独到解析，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">受邀亮相本次大会。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">iWorld</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">品牌由美国国际数据集团（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IDG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">）创办，首届博览会于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1985</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年在美国旧金山举办。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IDG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">iWorld</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">数字世界博览会引入中国，取得巨大成功。经过历届的积累，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">iWorld</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">已经成长为全球最具影响力的移动互联生态圈的盛会之一。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18-19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">iWorld 2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">举办了为期两天的国际高峰论坛，在“创新、定义、未来”主题下，围绕移动游戏、人工智能、信息安全、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">VR/AR</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">等重磅版块，发布市场最新调研成果和前瞻性观点，带来最具价值的行业发展讯息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日举办的移动游戏论坛上，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">与来自中外移动产业中的企业领袖、游戏研发人员齐聚一堂，针对移动游戏出海发展的机遇与挑战展开讨论。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic VP </span><span style=\"font-family:\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">姚志受邀出席本次论坛，一同参会的还有谷歌大中华区大客户部游戏行业总经理邓辉、易观智库高级研究总监薛永锋、中国手游娱乐集团执行副总裁张卫华、游戏茶馆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">王佳伦。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">随着中国移动游戏趋近饱和，面对竞争日渐激烈的国内市场，出海掘金逐渐成为移动开发者的必选题。面对广阔的海外游戏市场，姚志提到：“游戏出海需要关注产品质量、本地化、运营、支付和格局等五个维度。游戏品质固然重要，但是面对使用习惯差异巨大的海外市场，深度本地化仍是重中之重；要保持游戏持续的生命力，精细化运营则必不可少。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">圆桌论坛上，姚志与邓辉、薛永锋围绕游戏出海进行了深入的交流，在游戏本地化、出海游戏类型、目标市场选择、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">审查新政的影响、海外市场的差异化运营等方面进行了深度的剖析，探讨如何发展完善的移动游戏产业，为未来移动游戏的发展趋势和“出海”之路搭建一个国际化的全球产业沟通平台。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">对国内企业而言，海外市场机遇与挑战并存。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">成功帮助国内诸多企业完成了出海战略，沉淀了深厚的出海推广经验。凭借丰富的海外实战积累，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">将帮助更多开发者成功走出国门，实现“海外掘金”的全球化战略。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', null, '2', '8月19日，Eptonic VP姚志受邀参加iWorld移动游戏论坛。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('68', 'zh_cn', '畅聊合作共赢，Eptonic CJ之行完满收官', '   2016-08-01 | 中国 · 上海', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474452342.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic 2016 ChinaJoy</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">之行完满收官！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">36</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">场发布会、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">56</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">场行业峰会、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">75</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个同期酒会——</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ChinaJoy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大会日程紧凑。本届大会，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">派出了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人阵容，为期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">天的泛娱乐盛宴，精彩不间断，上海之行收获颇丰！</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>人气爆棚，携手共赢</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的展馆位于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">BTOB</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">W2-C201</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，全开放式展台迎来了众多海内外商务人士。我们分享了市场洞察和全球营销数据，帮助企业和开发者了解极具增长潜力的国家和地区，并为其制定切实可行的出海战略。面对潜力无限的海外市场，到访者纷纷表达出海意愿。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">天的时间，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">接待了海内外上百家企业，我们积极与各企业分享全球营销经验，并大力拓展海外推广渠道，展台保持着活跃的交流气氛。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">能力卓越，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">路前行</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年发展至今，短短两年的时间，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">迅速打响了品牌在业界的知名度，推广效果和服务品质得到了合作伙伴的一致认可。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的合作伙伴遍布世界各国，借本次展会的契机，我们与众多海外合作企业展开了面对面的沟通。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">来自美国、英国、俄罗斯、西班牙、以色列、乌克兰、荷兰及香港、澳门等地的合作伙伴到访</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的展台，与我们零距离交谈。交流过程中，我们可以感受到广告主对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">海外推广和优化能力的肯定，对合作渠道方</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">AM</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提供的一对一服务也加以赞赏。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>测试壕礼，助攻突围</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">经历红海厮杀后，开发者们逐渐将目光转移至海外市场，七月出台的“最严手游新规”更是增加了国内的市场阻力，出海发展势在必行。针对开发者的出海需求，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">准备了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">份价值</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">美元的海外推广测试包，每日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">份的礼包，受到了企业的欢迎，开展后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">小时内就被领取一空。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">完整的产品市场分析、产品本地化建议、热点地区分析、测试投放效果报告，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">助力国内开发者迅速实现困境突围。相信在今后的国际市场中，能看到更多从中国杀出的“黑马”。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>中韩大会，共话合作</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">应邀出席中（成都）韩游戏产业洽谈会。作为西南最大的出海推广企业，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">与数十家中韩互联网企业论道中韩手游发展趋势，共同展望两国手游合作的未来。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亚太区商务总监郑勇一分享了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的海外推广经验，并针对韩国市场进行了细致深入的分析。会后，郑勇一与韩国手游行业代表进行了商务洽谈，并达成了初步的合作意向。随着双方合作的不断深入，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将在韩国地区的数字营销中扮演着更加重要的角色。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">泛娱乐大趴结束了，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的征程仍在继续——从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ASW</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（拉斯维加斯）到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GMIC</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（北京），到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ChinaJoy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（上海），再到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ASE</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（纽约），</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的足迹已经遍布全球。我们将继续大步向前，在更多的世界顶级大会上登台亮相，与全球同行共同激发互联网出海变现新灵感。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">全球之行，从这里开始！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', null, '2', 'Eptonic 2016 ChinaJoy之行完满收官，本届大会，Eptonic派出了8人阵容，为期3天的泛娱乐盛宴，精彩不间断，上海之行收获颇丰！', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('68', 'en_us', 'China Digital Entertainment Expo&Conference 2016', '   2016-08-01 | Shanghai, China', null, '<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474452491.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\">China\nDigital Entertainment Expo&amp;Conference 2016 was held in Shanghai and Eptonic\nattended this conference.</span><br></p><p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">Located&nbsp; in\nW2-C201, Eptonic attracted many business people at home and abroad. </span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">We shared\nour insight in digital marketing and data analysis, helping enterprises to know\nmore about overseas emerging&nbsp; markets and\npromote overseas with our customized strategies.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', null, '1', '36 release conference, 56 industry conference and 75 parties-You can find all of these at this ChinaJoy 2016. Eptonic had achieved much by attending this conference.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('71', 'en_us', 'Eptonic was Awarded “The Best Mobile Advertising Company in 2016”', '       ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474274085.jpg\" style=\"width: 800px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">On September 8th-9th, 2016, the festival of big data.\nmobile marketing was held in Beijing and as the global leader in mobile\nintegrated marketing, Eptonic was invited to attend it.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">This festival\ngathered many leading advertising companies, marketing services companies,\nmedia and so on, dedicating to promoting the communication and cooperation of\nthe industry.<br></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">Based on its\nprofessional marketing service, customized advertising strategies, massive\nadvertising resources and affiliates, rich industry experience and leading\nadvertising service team, Eptonic was awarded “The Best Mobile Advertising Company\nin 2016”.<br></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">But this won’t\nstop us, we will keep on working hard to provide you with the best advertising\nservice.</font><br></p>', null, '1', 'From September 8th-9th, 2016, the festival of big data. mobile marketing was held in Beijing and Eptonic was proud to be awarded “The Best Mobile Advertising Company in 2016”.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('71', 'zh_cn', 'Eptonic揽获「2016年度最佳移动广告公司」奖', '       ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474274085.jpg\" style=\"width: 800px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日，由广告主传媒、品微会主办的「</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">大数据·移动营销节」在京隆重举行。作为移动营销行业的佼佼者，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">受邀参加了本次盛典。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">本次活动汇集了国内主流广告主的高管、广告公司、营销服务公司和媒体广告运营方面的负责人，旨在促进行业的发展与交流，并对移动营销领域的优秀企业和平台加以表彰。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日，主办方揭晓了备受瞩目的「移动营销金坐标奖」。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">作为行业领先移动推广平台，在数字营销领域收获了丰硕的成果，并凭借专业的推广技术和出色的创意得到了业界的一致认可，一举斩获「</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年度最佳移动广告公司」奖。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">作为行业领先的移动推广平台，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">凭借前瞻性的战略规划和市场定位布局海外市场，对接全球的渠道与广告主，依托丰富的海外营销经验，帮助他们创造更大的商业价值。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的极致海外推广能力，得到了广告主的一致肯定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">当前，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">在全球移动营销市场中取得了丰硕的成果，推广覆盖全球超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">个国家和地区，全球日展示量逾</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">亿次，已助力超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">和手游成功出海。未来，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">将继续深耕技术，创新营销，开拓移动营销新征程，并通过在全球范围内开展广泛合作，与广大伙伴携手开创海外共赢局面。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', null, '2', '第三节移动营销金坐标颁奖盛典上，Eptonic斩获“2016年度最佳移动广告公司”奖', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('72', 'en_us', 'Jeremy Yao was invited to have a speech at the mobile games forum.', '       ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474274306.jpg\" style=\"width: 497px;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Arial\">iWorld 2016, sponsored by IDG, was successfully held\nin New International Convention and Exhibition Center in Chengdu. This\nconference had gathered many representatives and leaders in the field of\ninternet and proudly, Eptonic was also invited to attend this conference.<br></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">At the\nconference, many forums have been held at the same time, including mobile\ngames, artificial intelligence, information security, VR/AR and so on, bringing\npeople with the latest insights and achievements.<br></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">Jeremy Yao, VP\nin Eptonic, was invited to have a speech at the mobile games forum. He shared\nhis deep insight in the promotion overseas for apps and mobile games from the\nperspective of localization, product quality, payment habits, local tradition\nand preference and so on.<br></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">Based on its rich industry\nexperience and professional promotion strategies, Eptonic has helped many\ndomestic companies to achieve overseas success, and will always try to do so.</font><br></p>', null, '1', 'On August 19th, 2016, Jeremy Yao, VP in Eptonic, was invited to have a speech at the mobile games forum of iWorld 2016.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('69', 'zh_cn', '在「突围」沙龙，和大咖们共话海内外破局之道', '  2016-06-28 | 中国 · 成都', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474373995.jpg\" style=\"width: 994px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日下午，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">联合</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Testin</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">主办的“突围·手游</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&amp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">应用海内外破局之道”主题沙龙圆满结束。来自移动互联网的行业大咖、业界代表与本地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">和发行齐聚一堂，就移动互联网在后手游</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&amp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">应用时代的发展方向进行了深入的交流和探讨。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">本次的沙龙共吸引来自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">多家公司的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">多名小伙伴，“突围”沙龙，不仅是行业经验分享会，也是移动互联网企业的交流合作平台。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">错过了本次沙龙的干货分享？不要紧，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">精心整理了本次活动精彩看点，为你回顾沙龙精华。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">结合国外玩法</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&amp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">国内经济系统，打造出海变现模式</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">蓝港互动集团</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> VP </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">王世颖认为，在当前的游戏市场中，鲜有游戏能够做到“全球通吃”，很多游戏在国内发展很好但是在海外市场遇冷，而很多在海外发展很好的产品在国内市场却表现平平。国内产品出海通常会遇到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大难题：产品本身、本地化、渠道、支付和市场。与国内相比，海外用户更倾向于轻量化的产品，针对手游出海，“国外用户喜欢的玩法</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">国内的经济系统”的模式，将在一定程度上保证产品的营收，给游戏带来可观的效益。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>欧美市场或成出海新标配</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">深海游戏</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> VP </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">袁悦在演讲中分享到，以前的东南亚是出海热潮，而在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年欧美将成为下一个标配。美国市场渠道单一，竞争相对稳定，欧洲拥有全球最大的移动游戏市场，整体市场规模、用户质量和收入都属顶尖级别。通过优化支付、深度本地化和全方位媒体覆盖等一系列的精细化运营方式，可以使游戏在欧美市场站稳脚跟。国内表现不够出色的游戏不妨在欧美地区进行推广，或能带来意想不到的收益。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>注重区域化特色是出海的必修课</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic VP </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">姚志认为国内市场越难越难做原因在于：手游市场趋于饱和、市场付费习惯尚未形成、维权手段匮乏以及运营能力的欠缺。放眼全球市场，目前仍存在诸多蓝海：墨西哥、印尼、土耳其等地存在巨大的市场潜力。游戏偏好上，南美追逐欧美潮流，偏爱格斗冒险类。作为新兴市场的东南亚，对武侠文化接受度较高，射击、格斗、卡牌类是主打。在海外市场做产品推广，本地化工作是重中之重，了解俄罗斯中意黑色的偏好，规避中东地区的宗教禁忌等区域化特色是出海的必修功课。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>学习优质产品的成功模式</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">自来也科技</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> CEO </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">包峰铭从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APP Store</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">榜单切入，对排名靠前的产品进行了详细的解读。榜单中表现优秀的游戏在游戏玩法、付费模式、题材等方面都有很多共通之处。付费游戏可以通过高质量、独到的创意在市场中杀出重围，对于付费游戏而言，移植其他平台的成功游戏也是个不错的选择。于免费游戏而言，则更需要注重把握时事以及休闲游戏的风向，通过“短平快”的产品以及理性的广告模式实现快速的变现。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>产品的价值核心是用户体验</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Testin CTO </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">李小川从产品测试环节和技术层面分享了提升用户体验的经验，李小川说到，我们可以通过手工检测和自动检测双重检测的方式，提前侦察产品问题，优化产品质量，从而减少因设备兼容性问题导致的用户流失问题，“价值核心是用户，我们需要最大化赚取人的价值，最大化赚取体验的价值”。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>无感知更新将最大程度留住用户</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卓盟科技</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> CEO </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">黄杲从产品热更、分包、加固三个角度分别阐述了产品运营对于维系用户的重要意义。每一次需要用户交互的更新都会造成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12%</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的用户流失，通过提升版本升级效率、加速产品迭代将有效解决这一问题。同时还可以通过分服更新、区域化更新、定向渠道更新等方式实现精细化运营，减少用户的感知，最大程度保护用户体验，从而减少因版本迭代产生的用户流失。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">圆桌论坛：当我们说手游</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&amp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">应用出海，我们在说些什么</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">游戏茶馆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> CEO </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">王佳伦主持的圆桌论坛，对出海业界关心的关注问题，如推荐的出海地区，推广渠道的选择、出海可能遇到的困难以及产品的海外发行进行了深入的探讨。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">袁悦认为题材是游戏出海最重要的元素，题材决定覆盖市场以及用户的留存，丧尸类题材的表现就非常出色。就出海地区而言，包峰铭认为南美市场是个不错的落脚点，许多大公司不愿意做南美市场，但是该地区用户量大，市场潜力无限，作为中小</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，可以先不考虑营收，以市场为主。谈到渠道，姚志认为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Adwords</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为世界级的推广平台，对出海推广举足轻重，而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">YouTube</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的视频广告表现也非常突出，利用时下热门的网红资源，可以实现新的营销突破。在出海推广中，也会遇到一些“坑”，王世颖认为，选择可靠的合作伙伴将会让出海之路更为顺畅。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">出海路遥，让我们打通所有环节，共同探寻新的海内外破局之道。今后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">还将举办多个行业交流分享会，让我们期待下次的相会！</span></p>', null, '2', '6月28日，Eptonic在成都天使咖啡主办了沙龙活动，移动互联网齐聚一堂，共谋困局突围之路。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('69', 'en_us', 'Breakthrough: Global Expansion Strategies of Mobile Games&Apps', '  2016-06-28 | Chengdu, China', null, '<p><span style=\"font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:楷体\" lang=\"EN-US\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474373995.jpg\" style=\"font-family: &quot;open sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei &quot;, sans-serif; width: 994px;\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">On June 28, 2016, we held a\nvery successful salon with Testin as the Joint sponsor.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">The salon had attracted more than 100\npartners from more than 70 companies and the industry representatives , local\nCP and publishers with the following points shared at this salon:</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">Firstly, in the global mobile games\nmarket, companies will encounter these five problems when promoting overseas:\nthe product itself, localization, channels, payment and markets.So, for this\nsituation, it can only help companies to achieve overseas success by combining\nthe foreign playing habits and domestic economic system.</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">Secondly, Europe and America market will\nstill be the preferential ones because of their market size, user quality and\nrevenue. By having payment optimization, depth localization and a full range of\nmedia coverage, companies can get an amazing profit.</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">Thirdly, location will be one of the most\nimportant factors when having overseas promotion. We need to know the local\npreference, tradition, buying habits, payment habits and so on to reach the\ntarget audience to the utmost. For example, as for the game preference, South\nAmerica loves the fighting and adventure games, following the trend in Europe\nand America, and for the emerging market-Southeast Asia, the people there have\nhigh acceptance of martial arts culture.</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Fourth, from the App store list, we can\nfind some common ways of playing the game, models of payment, game material and\nso on, so while devel</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">oping games, producers need to master the trend.</span></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">Fifth, improve user experience. “The\ncore of the value is user and we should acquire the value of users.” CTO in\nTestin said. We can measure the quality of the product in advance through the\nways of manual testing and automatic testing.</font></p>', null, '1', 'On June 28th, 2016, Eptonic held a salon, attracting many leading people in the field of mobile internet.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('77', 'en_us', 'Welcome Wendy Wu (Google Hong Kong) to visit Eptonic', ' On date May 20th, 2016, Wendy, advertising specialist in Google came by Eptonic and discussed the future cooperation deeply with us.', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474525056.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">On date May 20<sup>th</sup>, 2016, Wendy, advertising\nspecialist in Google came by Eptonic and she mainly shared the following ideas:<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">Firstly, She\nshared his insights in advertising affiliates, advertising techniques, and\nmarket development.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p><font face=\"Arial\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Secondly, “\nCreativity is the most important element to advertising, and great creativity\nhelps to promote conversion rate.” Wendy said. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Then she showed us the greatest examples for\nadvertising design from the world, which gave us insights into the strategy for\nthe optimized effect of the advertising. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></font></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">Thirdly, she\nalso spoke highly of Eptonic, including the professional team, advertising\nstrategies, and promotion performance.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">In the future,\nEptonic will keep on cooperating with Google, dedicating to improving\nadvertising performance and providing mobile internet companies with top\noverseas promotion service.</span><br></p>', null, '1', ' On date May 20th, 2016, Wendy, advertising specialist in Google came by Eptonic and discussed the future cooperation deeply with us.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('77', 'zh_cn', '谷歌伙伴到访Eptonic，携手共创未来', '   ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474525056.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日，来自谷歌公司的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wendy</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">到访了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，对移动出海推广问题进行交流，并对未来的战略合作进行了深入的探讨。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为资深的谷歌广告投放专家，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wendy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">侃侃而谈——从新一代的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Firebase</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，到广告渠道的选择，她讲述了自己在广告投放技巧和市场拓展方面的经验，并与现场小伙伴积极互动。</span><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wendy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">高度肯定了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的国际化推广团队，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的推广实力，在整个谷歌平台中表现也十分抢眼，受到业界的一致认可。</span><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">“创意是广告的关键，优秀的广告创意能大幅度提升广告转化率。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Wendy</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">表示。随后她逐一展示了谷歌平台上表现亮眼的创意案例，对于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的广告创意以及投放效果，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wendy</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">给予了很高的评价。</span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">未来，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">将继续与谷歌携手，共同致力于优化广告效果，为更多移动互联网公司提供优质的出海推广服务，助力企业实现品牌“全球化”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', null, '2', '来自谷歌公司的Wendy到访了Eptonic，对移动出海推广问题进行交流，并对未来的战略合作进行了深入的探讨。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('78', 'en_us', 'ADMEN Interview: Precipitation is for better outbreak', 'On May 19th, 2016, Jason Cao, CEO of Eptonic was interviewed for deep insights in overseas promotion strategies for domestic companies.', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474525571.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">On May 19th, 2016, Jason Cao, CEO\nof Eptonic was interviewed for deep insights in overseas promotion strategies\nfor domestic companies, and he mainly shared the following ideas:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>Firstly, he introduced Eptonic’s establishment and development briefly\nand the company’s four business platforms and some well-known successful\npromotion products.</p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Secondly, “You will find less opportunities, but more potential markets\noverseas.”, he said. Jason Cao thought there were mainly three advantages in\nforeign markets: Foreign media are more canonical and loyal, so it is easier to\ncommunicate; Foreign users have better payment habits than that of domestic;\nThe policies and regulations are more perfect.</span>&nbsp;</p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Thirdly, he also thought that China is in the leading position as for\nthe mobile internet, so China has a great advantage in overseas markets.</span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Fourth, Europe and the United States market and Southeast Asia market\nare still be the main ones for domestic companies, but meanwhile there are many\nopportunities in some developing countries.</span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Fifth, Even there are many opportunities, there exit many challenges,\nincluding product development and promotion.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>Finally, he explained Eptonic’s\ndevelopment plan in 2016, that was to shape company brand with its professional\nadvertising team, deep insight in target markets, rich advertising and\naffiliates resources and powerful technical advantages.</p>', null, '1', 'On May 19th, 2016, Jason Cao, CEO of Eptonic was interviewed for deep insights in overseas promotion strategies for domestic companies.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('70', 'zh_cn', 'morketing专访Eptonic曹远强：8年，沉淀了对流量的深度理解', '         ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">做一个事情，如果要做到无可替代，最无懈可击的就是在时间的长河中，用无数的实践去沉淀对于这个事情的深度理解，以形成敏锐有效的处理能力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">无论是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">端的站长时代，还是移动互联网的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">App</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Web</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">生态，有个本质的东西始终贯穿其中，即“流量”。对移动互联网和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">来说，有流量，并不等于能有效发挥作用；企业，需要流量，也不等于他能有效获得流量。专业的事情，还需要专业的人来干，而专业的人，并非一定是具有天生的优势，也许一个偶然，走进这个领域，然后踏踏实实扎进去干，用一种较真的态度，这也是实力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">移动互联网，这个本身具有全球化属性的时代，对于很多厂商来说，更多的考虑并不是如何活下去，而是如何壮大，这时，精准的海外推广和变现成为关键。在这个大势下，海外流量运作，催生了不少移动互联网新型创业者。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">就是其一，事实上，他们算是后入者，优势看上去并不那么明显，但是却出乎意料的成功，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic CEO </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">曹远强阐述：“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">真正启动在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年年底，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年就做到年营收</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">亿人民币。而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年的第一季度营收就已经做到了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">全年的水平”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">那么，作为一个后入者，曹远强凭什么在一两年做到这个成绩？答案：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年广告行业的沉淀和对于流量的深刻理解。他说，流量是互联网企业的生存之本。作为出海营销服务公司，不仅要给广告主提供其要求的数量，也要达到广告主满意的用户质量和效果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>全球移动互联网，中国走在了世界的前面</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">“早期国内广告市场比较混乱，所以一直以来，我们没有涉足国内市场。海外市场必然越来越大，对于海外广告推广的需求也会越来越大。移动互联网是自带全球属性的。国内移动互联网市场已经成为红海，很难再有发展空间，而国外却另一番天地”曹远强说。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">曹远强分析海外市场的优势：由于海外媒体相对更具有契约精神，沟通更加直接高效；海外用户的付费习惯远超于国内用户，且一些国家的政策法规也更加完善；再加上世界范围内没有太多疯狂的搅局者。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">对于多数出海游戏厂商而言，更多地考虑的并不是如何活下去，而是如何发展壮大。精准的海外推广和产品海外变现成为关键。在移动互联上，中国更多是走在了世界的前面，包括印度、巴西等市场要落后于中国市场的发展。因此，在海外分发上中国企业还很有竞争力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">另外，曹远强从区域市场进行了分析，欧美市场和东南亚市场是中国产品出海的主战场，另外，针对不同的客户，一些发展中国家的市场也非常大，这些国家用户量很可观，且处于功能机向智能机的过渡过程，很多广告形式都有很好的表现，但这些国家的变现通道尚不明朗，因此目前很多急于变现的产品（例如游戏类</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">App</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">）还没有大范围进入这种国家，但是一些工具应用类产品，以抢占用户市场为目的的公司，已经开始全面进入了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">启动前的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年沉浸</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">“之前，在互联网广告行业沉浸太多年了。从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic 14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年年底启动到今天，市场对我们的认可非常高，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年我们才算真正以公司的身份站出来”曹远强说。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">他分享到：“我是土生土长成都人，西南科技大学经济管理学院毕业，专业和互联网不沾边。个人没什么互联网和海外背景，外语也一般，做全球移动出海营销服务，更多的是个人兴趣，或者说机缘巧合”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">据了解，曹远强</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">08</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年进入互联网广告行业。大学时期曾以个人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Affiliate</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">进入互联网海外推广，他的合伙人何进也在那时一起进入这个行业。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">08</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年后，小工作室方式作为渠道角色全面进入海外推广。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10-12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年，获得雅虎</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">RightMedia</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的全球一级代理权限。他回顾，当时熬更守夜的研究了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">个月算法，通过自己的优化算法，使得发展非常迅速，并进一步开始了与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DoubleClick</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">等全球性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">exchange</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的合作，借助在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">exchange</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的技术经验积累，团队于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年全面做了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook Ads</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Adwords</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">精准推广项目，这些沉淀最终在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年底凝结成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，以公司的形式开始进入大家的视野。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">成立到现在，参与了多款明星</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">App</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的海外推广</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年底正式开业后，刚好遇上整个海外互联网广告的高速发展期。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareas