;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">他补充，我们对于“一站式服务”、“全套解决方案”这两个词语的理解非常深刻。而大部分的客户对于互联网海外广告的理解有一定的不足。投入产出比无疑是众多企业最为在意的出海关键，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">对症下药，从出海企业最为关心的“核心点”上入手，解决他们的困惑。“价格、质量、效果是客户最关注的”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">作为出海渠道，目前</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">海外投放国家超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">个，海外投放项目数百个，优质流量渠道数百家，每日超过百亿次展示，每月千万级海外安装，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">海外合作伙伴数百家，覆盖全球的移动网民。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年及未来的布局</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">从资本层面来看，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日拿了天使轮，当时只有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">多个员工，至今，公司团队已达近百人规模。近期，计划进行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">轮融资。曹远强分享，整个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年几乎只做老客户的业务，低调做事就行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年我们计划把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">公司的品牌推出去，让更多的新客户、新渠道、新朋友认识和了解我们。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年将是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的“品牌年”，公司将加大在品牌上的投入。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">至于对公司的展望，希望可以在全球海外推广行业稳稳的立足，同时在行业里建立良好的口碑，把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的优秀服务做到极致，让客户可以口碑相传。另外，未来一两年内，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">会整合全球流量资源，加快媒体渠道的本地化，从而获得高质量用户，有效地进行移动广告实时采买投放及优化。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">最后，曹远强分享了这两年来的创业心得：“互联网广告让我收获了人生第一桶金，并且带给我事业上第一份成就。以前认为自己是一个流量买卖的生意人，但经过这么多年后，逐渐有了更多的想法”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', null, '2', '做一个事情，如果要做到无可替代，最无懈可击的就是在时间的长河中，用无数的实践去沉淀对于这个事情的深度理解，以形成敏锐有效的处理能力。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('70', 'en_us', 'Morketing Interview: Jason Cao shared his deep insights in traffic ', '         ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474451304.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">Jason Cao, CEO of Eptonic, was interviewed by\nMorketing on May 6th, 2016 for deep understanding of the traffic and the reason\nwhy Eptonic can be so successful even only being established in 2014.</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">\nFirstly, he analyzed the advantages of overseas markets: communication is more\ndirect and efficient because overseas media relatively has more contract\nspirit; the paying habits of overseas users are much better than domestic users’;\nnational policies and regulations are also more perfect.</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">\nSecondly, he also gave his analysis from the regional market. Europe and the\nUnited States market and Southeast Asian market is the main battlefield of\nChina\'s overseas promotion.However, the market is very large in some developing\ncountries because of its user quantity and its status of advertising\ndevelopment.</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">\nLastly,He shared how Eptonic was established and how it was developing so\nquickly in the world and also the main business of Eptonic and some very\nsuccessful products it had promoted.</font></span><br></p>', null, '1', 'Jason Cao, CEO of Eptonic, was interviewed by Morketing on May 6th, 2016 for deep understanding of the traffic and the reason why Eptonic can be so successful even only being established in 2014.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('80', 'en_us', 'DOGAME Interview: Keep forward on the way for promoting overseas', '    ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474526092.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">On March 18, 2016, Jeremy Yao, VP in Eptonic was\ninterviewed by DOGAME for deep insights in the overseas promotion strategies\nand what can Eptonic bring to domestic companies that have global development\nplan.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">And the following was the real record of this\ninterview:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Q1: DOGAME</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">What business and\nresources advantages Eptonic has to help domestic companies to achieve overseas\nsuccess?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Jeremey Yao: Eptonic has three business platforms,\nthat is Eptonic Mediabuy</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">MDSP(Mobile Demand-side Platform )</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">EMN(Eptonic Media\nNetwork). As the leading platform for promoting overseas for mobile internet\ncompanies, Eptonic helps to acquire high quality users based on its depth data\nanalysis, precise user orientation and advanced technology.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Q2: DOGAME</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">As we all know that the\nbiggest problem for game start up companies is to acquire high quality traffic,\nfor this part, what can Eptonic do?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Jeremey Yao: Based on years of experience, Eptonic has\nmore than hundreds of overseas quality affiliates covering global users.\nBesides, Eptonic has established long and stable cooperation with some leading\nmedia platforms, like Facebook and Google. Three typical successful products(Flash\nKeyboard</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift\nwifi</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Power\nClean) can prove our strength.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Q3: DOGAME</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">What is Eptonic going to\ndo for domestic companies?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Jeremey Yao: Eptonic will hold many salons related to\noverseas promotion across the country to bring the latest industry information\nand customized promotion scheme.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Q4: DOGAME</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">What does Eptonic think\nabout the overseas app advertising development?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Jeremey Yao: There are many opportunities in foreign\ncountries, since their policies and regulations are relatively more perfect,\nand also overseas users have better payment habits.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Q5: DOGAME</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">How does Eptonic achieve\noverseas precision marketing?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Jeremey Yao: Eptonic has precision orientation\ntechnology , deep analysis for users interest and habits, rich advertising\nresources and affiliates to help improve conversion rate.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Q6: DOGAME</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">What are the advantages\nof Eptonic?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Jeremey Yao: Eptonic has the most excellent industry\nspecialists, customized promotion scheme, and powerful technical support.<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><o:p></o:p></font></span></p>', null, '1', 'On March 18th, 2016, Jeremy Yao, VP in Eptonic was interviewed by DOGAME for deep insights in the overseas promotion strategies and what Eptonic can bring to domestic companies.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('80', 'zh_cn', 'DOGAME专访Eptonic商务总监姚志：扬帆出海，E路前行', '    ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474526092.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">谈到手游的海外推广，很多厂商“不明觉厉”，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">游戏寒冬期，已经有国内的团队把手游出海作为出路。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在刚刚结束的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DOGAME</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">汇游戏行业沙龙现场，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DOGAME</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">游戏兵工厂有幸采访到了本次活动赞助商，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成都邑动科技商务总监姚志先生，他表示移动互联网是国际性的，也是未来互联网企业发展的大势所趋，要做到真正的国际化，还有很长的路要走，而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为全球领先的海外推广平台，是企业布局全球化的重要选择。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">姚志，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Jeremy.Yao</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">商务总监，毕业于四川大学，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年互联网</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IT</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">工作经验，曾就职于百度、凤凰传媒等公司，担任市场推广总监。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年跨界到互联网广告营销领域，致力于帮助更多的国内企业扩展海外市场，拥有丰富的海外推广经验及众多国际优秀客户的好评。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">出海推广领航者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">：助力出海，精准通达</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年布局海外战略，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年已形成国际先进的海外业务平台，接入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">国际主流量广告平台，为广告主提供的不仅是获得最低价格展示和最优质流量的渠道服务，还有更多的增值服务和本地化定制服务。客户包括了国内应用类、手游类和跨境电商类客户中所有重要的广告主，已助力百度、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APUS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">360Security</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Clean Master</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等行业在海外市场的拓展方面取得显著成绩，成长为世界先进的移动广告出海领航者。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">以下是专访整理实录分享内容：</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">DOGAME</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年布局出海推广平台，目前有哪些业务功能及资源能够帮助游戏厂商出海营销的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">姚志：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">旗下有三大平台</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic\nMediabuy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MDSP(Mobile Demand-side Platform </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">移动需求方平台</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMN(Eptonic\nMedia Network </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">广告交易私有平台</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为国际领先的移动出海渠道商，通过深度数据挖掘分析、精细用户人群定向、广告实时竞价、全球精准投放技术为支撑，帮助企业快速获取海量用户及流量变现。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">DOGAME</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：游戏创业公司出海最大难题是优质流量如何获取，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在这方面是怎样解决的呢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">姚志：现阶段，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">海外投放国家超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个，海外投放项目超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个，优质流量渠道数百家，每日超过百亿次展示，每月千万级海外下载安装，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">海外合作伙伴数百家，覆盖全球的移动网民。业务覆盖全球，我们主要与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Goolge</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这些国际主流量平台合作，以及我们众多优质网盟，拥有丰富的流量媒介资源。例如我们代理的三款产品，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flash Keyboard</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift wifi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Power Clean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在海外的推广都取得了很不错的成绩，尤其是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flash Keyboard </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月份在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Play</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">免费排行榜取得了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Top 4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的优秀成绩，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift Wifi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">也是超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">万的全球用户和两千万的分享</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wifi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">热点数。据第三方数据公司</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">App Annie</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">统计，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">刚上线</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个月，就登顶</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">33</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家工具类应用榜，进入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">66</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家的工具类应用榜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TOP5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，拿下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">81</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家工具类应用榜前十名的好成绩。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">DOGAME</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：赞助</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Dogame</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">汇游戏行业沙龙活动，为国内</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">走向海外市场打下基础，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">还会有哪些扶持政策给到国内的创业公司</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">姚志：很高兴与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DOGAME</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">汇的沙龙合作，这样的活动对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">及行业伙伴们的交流合作非常有意义，今年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会在全国范围内会举办出海沙龙活动，计划地区有北京、上海、成都、广州、深圳、厦门、台湾等地区，邀请全国众多</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">及发行以及权威数据机构、行业媒体出席活动，共同就“如何出海”等专题进行行业剖析，并带给更多的国内创业公司出海经验分享以及为其企业量身定制出海营销方案。。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">DOGAME</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对海外</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">广告这块发展趋势是怎么看的呢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">姚志：国内移动互联网环境，经过近几年的激烈竞争的角逐，很难有市场发展空间。而海外市场环境，由于海外媒体相对更具有契约精神，沟通也更加直接高效，且一些国家的政策法规也更加完善，再加上世界范围内没有太多疯狂的搅局者，因而相对国内还是干净许多。比如成功占据</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Play</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">世界榜单</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Top 5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Clean Master</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，其实一直不乏中国团队产品闪耀世界的例子。近期更有狂飙突进的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Apus Launcher</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，仅半年多的时间就实现了全球</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿以上的安装量，并跻身</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Play</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">全球应用榜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Top 10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，使得这个仅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人不到的团队，估值水涨船高超过了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿美金。这一切都越来越证明，现如今一个有竞争力的团队，一个优秀的产品，若想在最短的时间里证明自己的话，出海真的是一个行之有效的方式。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">DOGAME</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是通过哪些技术实现海外精准营销的呢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">姚志：从技术上，运用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MDSP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的精准定位广告和个人兴趣行为再定向技术，覆盖了全球化的广告资源和媒介购买技术，会给企业提供全方面的整合网络营销解决方案，从而做到用户体验及转化最大化。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">DOGAME</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">拥有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">渠道资源，同类公司也在积极进军中国市场，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">相较这些公司有什么样的优势</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">姚志：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">拥有资深的行业团队、专业的媒体策略、领先的创意设计以及强大的技术支持。我们的核心优势：第一，大量的投放实战锻炼出了一支高水平的全球一流投放团队，拥有丰富的投放经验和高超的投放技巧</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">其次，可以实现在全球范围内短时间快速上量，以快速、精准、效果满足合作需求，让客户在最短时间内看到效果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第三，以技术作为驱动力跟踪用户的动作，协助开发商延长产品的生命周期。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>总结：</b>但对于多数出海游戏厂商而言，更多地考虑的并不是如何活下去，而是如何发展壮大。精准的海外推广和产品海外变现成为关键。在移动互联上，中国更多是走在了世界的前面，包括印度、巴西等市场要落后于我国市场发展一到两年。所以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">认为在海外分发上中国企业是很有竞争力的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">已经开启了新一轮的奋斗征途，扩大布局，从多个领域助力中国乃至全球企业实现国际化，并推动中国企业在海外市场竞争新格局的形成，与游戏厂商及全球合作伙伴在新趋势下进行交流与碰撞。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', null, '2', '路演活动后，Eptonic商务总监姚志接受了DOGAME的独家专访', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('81', 'en_us', 'Eptonic was Invited to Attend ChinaBang Adwards Ceremony', '   ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474526467.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font color=\"#636363\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font color=\"#636363\"><br></font></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">On March 31, 2016, ChinaBang Adwards ceremony with TechNode\nas the sponsor was successfully held in Chengdu and Eptonic was proud to\nannounce that it was invited to attend this ceremony.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;“With innovation\nas the soul, and science and technology as the backbone”,this ceremony gathered\nmany domestic start-up companies.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Based on\nadvantaged technology, professional advertising service team and customized\npromotion scheme, Eptonic stood out and won the praise of the industry. Jeremy\nYao, VP in Eptonic accepted the award on behalf on the company.</span><br></p>', null, '1', 'On March 31st, 2016, ChinaBang Adwards ceremony with TechNode as the sponsor was successfully held in Chengdu and Eptonic was proud to announce that it was invited to attend this ceremony.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('81', 'zh_cn', 'Eptonic受邀参加ChinaBang Adwards颁奖盛典', '   ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474526467.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font color=\"#636363\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font color=\"#636363\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font color=\"#636363\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">ChinaBang Awards</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一直以“发现中国创新的力量”为宗旨，积极在全中国范围内搜寻最有潜力、最有价值的创业项目，力求打造行业内最权威的评选盛会。</span></font><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日，由动点科技</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TechNode</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">主办并发起的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ChinaBang\nAdwards</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">颁奖盛典在成都圆满落幕，作为西南创新企业代表，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">受主办方邀请参加了本次活动。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“创新为魂，科技立城”，本次活动聚焦中国创业公司出海，关注亚洲创新新势力。作为行业领先的移动出海推广平台，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">秉持着“勇于开拓、敢于创新、精益求精”的精神，在企业发展的过程中，踏实稳步地前行。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以专业的技术、优质的服务，在行业内树立了良好的口碑。在已有的业务基础上，我们通过不断优化广告投放技术，全力打造一流的服务质量，走在行业的前沿。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将持续发力，继续提升服务品质，力求为开发者提供更优质、更专业的广告投放策略及服务，为国内优秀产品出海保驾护航。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">颁奖盛典后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ChinaBang</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">评选组委会选择</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">公司作为创新企业代表，携手投资方，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日上午，对商业模式和企业文化进行了实地考察，并与公司领导进行了亲切友好的交流。</span></p>', null, '2', '与Eptonic一起发现中国创新的力量', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('82', 'en_us', 'Ignite The Night', '  2016-04-28 | Beijing, China', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474526785.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">On April 28, 2016, the top party -”Ignite The Night”\nwas held in Beijing together with GMIC conference, with APUS as the main\nsponsor and Eptonic as the silver sponsor, gathering many partners in the\nindustry of mobile internet.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>More than 3000\npeople crowded into the place to enjoy the big party.</p><p>You would find\nhere: all kinds of drinks and food, and many beauties and the handsome.</p><p>This was for\nyou to put aside your work and worries and enjoy the relaxation and happiness\nat this time.<br></p>', null, '1', 'On April 28th, 2016, a big party in the industry of mobile internet was held in Beijing.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('82', 'zh_cn', 'GMIC期间全行业第一大趴，跨夜狂欢', '   2016-04-28 | 中国 · 北京', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474526785.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">APUS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">斥百万巨资，独家打造互联网行业</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Party\nTop One </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">——“燃·</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Ignite The Night</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">”，互联网行业第一</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Party</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">在各界盛情期待下，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日晚神秘亮相！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">作为银牌赞助商，与一众行业伙伴共同加入了激情狂欢！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在北京最时尚最具人气的夜店里，我们接受了全互联网人的拥抱，原定</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个人的场地，挤满了近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人！我们很挤，重点是每一位都很嗨！这一晚不仅是现场的火爆，也刷爆了整个行业的朋友圈！</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">全</span>行业的小伙伴都在这儿——派对现场，人潮涌动，直至酒吧门外！丢掉报告，甩开座谈，让我们嗨翻屋顶！燃动业界，共享别样夜晚。香醇美酒，精致佳肴，让我们尽享此刻！硬汉还有辣妹，劲歌还有热舞，燃动躁动，热情弥漫。</p>', null, '2', 'Eptonic支持的行业趴燃动京城，吸引了众多业界精英加盟。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('73', 'en_us', 'Interview: Eptonic achieves to become the best platform for advertising promotion', '          ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474274458.jpg\" style=\"width: 497px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">Jim, COO of Eptonic, was interviewed on May 26, 2016\nfor deep understanding of the ways for acquiring high quality overseas users, promoting\nin target markets, and achieving the best traffic monetizing.</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">\nFirstly, he introduced the establishment and development of Eptonic briefly.\nEptonic was established in 2014, and combined with the trend of promoting\noverseas of domestic internet enterprises and big investment, it developed\nextremely quickly.</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">\nSecondly, He owned Eptonic’s success to the following reasons:<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">Employing those who have strong potentiality and\nlearning ability and focusing on employees’ professional accomplishment.</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">\nIntegrating the industry resources and having long stable cooperation with\nFacebook and Google.</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">\nHaving much experience and long accumulation as for advertising optimization\nand affiliate coverage.</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">\nCreating professional overseas promotion strategies to acquire the target\naudience.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Based on all of the above reasons, Eptonic had\nhelped many domestic companies to achieve oversea success, take the product of\nFlash Keyboard, Swift Wifi, and Power Clean and so on.</span><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Finally, he said in the\nyear 2016, Eptonic will keep on cooperating with more global famous media, and\nproviding customer with the best professional service.</font></span><br></p>', null, '1', 'Jim, COO of Eptonic, was interviewed on May 26th, 2016 for deep understanding of the ways for acquiring high quality overseas users, promoting in target markets, and achieving the best traffic monetiz', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('79', 'zh_cn', '白鲸专访曹远强：解谜Swift WiFi背后推手——Eptonic', '   ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474525921.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">移动互联网全球化概念，不断地冲击着踏进这家公司的人——亮白的主色调，把天花板上蜿蜒的蓝色线条凸显出来，简单却极具视觉冲击；蓝色和彩色的世界地图在巧妙的设计下，出现在拜访者的视觉中心。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这里是成都市天府软件园</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">C11</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的成都办公室。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">也是全球成绩卓越的产品</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flash Keyboard</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的海外推手。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>总收入突破千万美金的创业公司</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">注册成立，以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">曹远强为首的几个创始人，都在该公司即将开展的业务——数字营销，服务跨屏广告和移动互联网广告推广这些领域，积累了近六年的经验，有了固定的客户和成功案例。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“做为扎根国内耕耘海外的移动互联网公司，我希望有一天能在中国建立一个世界性的推广平台。”曹远强说，他们拥有丰富的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SEO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">服务经验以及众多海外媒体渠道，为什么不在传统媒体的行业经验上，将移动互联网及海外众多优质媒体进行融合，催生新的应用模式？</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">诞生了。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">公司注册完成后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">就签约了十几款产品准备在全球市场开始推广，并与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等建立了稳定的战略合作关系。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">现在，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有数百家海外合作伙伴，覆盖全球的移动互联网用户海外投放。“国家超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个，海外投放项目超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个，优质流量渠道数百家，每日展示百亿次以上，每月千万级海外下载安装。”在公司刚成立时，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">只有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个人，</span>\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">而现在迅速扩大至百人规模。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">已获得数千万人民币天使轮融资，获得资本市场青睐，截至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年末，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">总收入突破千万美金。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>顺势而行，移动互联网海外推广大有可为</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">曹远强对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SEO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SEM</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Social Media Marketing</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Media Buy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等领域的研究，已有近八年时间。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，新传播生态下的商业逻辑悄然诞生，国际移动广告增长率直线上升，移动广告已经慢慢取代传统广告，媒体组织架构发生悄然改变，传统</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">互联网形式的全媒体已深度融合，在市场推广上发生巨大的冲击。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">中国市场是全球最大的单一市场，但是也是较为混乱和复杂的市场，很多国内企业因为过度竞争激发了“出海狂潮”。近几年，已诞生了许多成功的中国出海公司。与国内市场相比，海外市场更加规范有序，生态更完善，海外用户，尤其是欧美用户的付费习惯远超国内用户。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">八年里，曹远强亲身经历着这一变革，在经验中摸索出独特的海外推广方法论。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对每一个产品都会做深入的研究和挖掘，结合产品原有功能设计广告位。“对于开发者来说，既赚了钱，对用户体验也是零伤害。对广告商来说，广告位不仅广告形式上跟产品完全融合，实际上就是产品的功能。”曹远强认为，全球化是未来移动互联网的大趋势，移动互联网海外推广大有可为。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">移动互联网是个特别平等开放的领域，有中国公司走向世界，也就有海外公司来中国掘金。同理，有中国公司到海外其他市场推广，其他国家的公司也有这个需求。所以，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">构建起来的，是服务于全球公司间的推广平台。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><b>继续深耕东南亚和北美市场</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“未来一两年内，我们会整合全球流量资源，加快媒体渠道的本地化，从而获得高质量用户，有效地进行移动广告实时采买投放及优化。”</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在采访中，我们聊到了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年计划。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">曹远强提出有谋出动，稳步发展，在东南亚已经取得了一些市场突破和成绩，而北美作为重点攻破对象，曹远强曾多次前往美国，与国外极具影响力的权威公司就业务合作问题进行深入洽谈，获取大量的业务资源，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将持续深耕东南亚和北美市场作为重要战略方向。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“和同类公司相比，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的主要优势在于高质量的流量和专业的技术团队所带来的金牌服务和口碑，我们会利用我们的优势整合不同的媒体形式，为客户提供更加深入而全方位的服务，以使客户的海外推广达到最好的效果。”曹远强说，这也是为什么</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">能拿下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flash Keyboard</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Swift WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">代理的主要原因。“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，我们将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的业务根据不同的产品进行精确的细分，更好的服务客户。”</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目前宣布已完成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">万人民币的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">轮融资，在全球已有超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">万的全球用户和两千万的分享</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wifi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">热点数。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">App Annie</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">统计，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">刚上线</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个月，就登顶</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">33</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家工具类应用榜，居</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">66</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家的工具类应用榜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TOP5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，拿下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">81</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家工具类应用榜前十名的好成绩。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flash\nKeyboard</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">高居</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Play</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">美国免费工具类应用排名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TOP4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">360 Security</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APUS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Du Battery Saver</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Du Speed</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Clean Master</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">……这些产品在海外市场的榜单成绩背后，都有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的参与。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目前，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的海外推广团队</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MediaBuy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">为主打力量，专注于在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上进行精准广告投放以及优化。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMN</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MDSP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以及原生广告等业务也在顺利开展，并一致获得客户好评。未来，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">也将开拓跨境电商的海外推广服务。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对于未来，曹远强非常有信心。“作为移动出海的操盘手，以顺势之力，为广告主带来更高的投资回报率，而获取的流量直接转化货币。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有信心，在国内乃至全球移动广告领域，占据一席之地。”</span></p>', null, '2', '白鲸社区专访曹远强，全面解读成功产品背后的海外推手。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('73', 'zh_cn', '大成网专访何进：打造移动互联网全球化的广告平台', '          ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474274458.jpg\" style=\"width: 50%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年开始，移动互联网全球市场成为一片蓝海。移动出海俨然已经成为一种行业趋势，越来越多的企业也开始将目光投到全球市场。但出海淘金看似充满了诱惑，实则暗流涌动，机遇与风险并存，面临着一系列的问题需要解决。如何获取优质的海外用户？如何结合目标市场制定有针对性的推广计划？如何将流量实现最大程度的变现？位于成都天府软件园的移动出海推广公司，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的创始人何进，接受了大成网的专访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">顺势而生，抢占先机</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的海外业务规划始于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，当时，国内互联网企业成为出海主力，涌现大规模的出海热潮，掀起了全球化海外格局。何进和曹远强拥有近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年的移动广告经验和市场资源积累，两位创始人决定组建团队，进军海外。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的成立可以说是应时而生。这种新颖的商业模式，也使得</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">很快得到了资本的垂青。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">拿到了千万级的天使轮投资。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“公司正式开始运营实际上是从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年开始，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年是一个非常恰当的切入时间点，太早的话市场还不是很成熟，太晚则过于激烈。”何进表示，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年从大的角度来看，国内移动平台的格局已经相对稳定，而海外市场则呈现蓬勃发展的趋势。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">相比国内用户，海外用户更乐于付费与分享、用户忠诚度高。“我们希望帮助众多想要出海淘金的中国开发者们，在全球范围内获取优质用户，并在用户达到一定基数后提供高效的流量变现方案。”何进说道。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>机遇与挑战并存，创业门槛高</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">高速增长往往会给公司带来各种各样的问题，创始人也将承受巨大的压力和挑战。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“为了给广告主提供专业的海外推广服务，不管是在人员配置优化还是资源整合布局方面，我们都做了充分的准备。”</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一、填补市场人才缺口</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">业务逐步扩大，顶级技术人才的吸收与纳入，成为公司关注的一个重点。但由于当时移动互联网出海产业正处于新兴阶段，专业人员极其匮乏，招聘一度处于尴尬期。在这种情况下，两位创始人果断决定启用一些有潜力，学习能力强的新人，亲自培养，并且投入大量的时间和精力提高员工的专业度及专业素养。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二、优质资源整合，全面进军海外市场。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">何进和曹远强以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年多海外经验沉淀，积累大量优质资源，曾多次前往海外进行企业拜访与考察，优先整合优质渠道，与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">google</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">建立了长期稳定的合作战略，亲身见证国际化趋势。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>怎么帮助移动应用和游戏获取全球用户？</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">360 Security</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APUS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Du Battery\nSaver</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Du Speed Booster</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Clean Master</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">……这些产品在海外市场耀眼的榜单成绩背后，都有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的参与。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">何进认为，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">主要优势在于海外移动推广以及变现方案的制定和优化，特别是在广告优化能力和渠道覆盖能力上，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有着较为深厚的积累。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一直以高质量的流量和专业的技术服务国内企业，利用技术优势整合不同的优质资源，为客户提供更加深入的全方位服务，使客户的海外推广达到最好的效果。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“我们很乐意为每一位合作伙伴提供我们所掌握的市场信息，以协助他们顺利开拓出海业务。”何进表示。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">专业的服务以及高效的推广，让</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的海外业务迅速在业内打响。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">已经形成了成熟全面的出海体系，可满足广告主的多元化需求。如今，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">已有四大业务体系，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Mediabuy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMN</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MDSP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以及原生广告，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">现有数百家海外合作伙伴，流量覆盖的国家和地区已经超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个，海外投放项目超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个，优质流量渠道数百家，每日展示百亿次以上，每月千万级海外下载安装。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推广的三款明星产品，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flash\nKeyboard</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift wifi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Power Clean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在海外的推广都获得了不错的成绩。比如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flash Keyboard </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月份在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Play</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">免费排行榜取得了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Top 4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的优秀成绩，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift Wifi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">也是超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">万的全球用户和两千万的分享</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wifi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">热点数。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">据第三方数据公司</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">App Annie</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">统计，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">刚上线</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个月，就登顶</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">33</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家工具类应用榜，进入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">66</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家的工具类应用榜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TOP5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，拿下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">81</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家工具类应用榜前十名的好成绩。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">LionMobi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">公司旗下的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Power Clean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月推广至今，在海外获得</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">270</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿次曝光量、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿点击量、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">万的安装量，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月上旬，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PowerClean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">首获</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Play</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推荐，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月中旬，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PowerClean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">又连续斩获</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">次</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GooglePlay</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推荐。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">LionMobi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的合作还多次在包括</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">F8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在内的会议中被</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做为经典案例进行分享。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">移动出海市场巨大，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">全面部署</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">何进认为，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年移动互联网行业“出海”的需求将呈现喷井之势。整个移动互联网产业仍然保持着非常强劲的发展势头，驱动着整个全球互联网和新兴技术的创新与变革。　</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会对自己的海外流量资源进行全方位的整合。”面对市场的变化，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年将扩大与全球知名媒体及区域优势媒体的合作范围，如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等，都已经成为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">重要的合作伙伴。团队将进一步整合这些媒体资源，为广告主提供更具成效的营销方案；同时，团队计划加大技术和人员投入，根据不同行业的营销需求，提供定制化的营销策略，根据不同地域的流量情况部署流量运营计划。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“全球的最大的创新浪潮就是移动互联网领域。这个浪潮中，应该说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">彻底抓住了这个机遇，在可预计的将来，我相信</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可以成为移动出海领域的领航者。“何进对公司未来的发展充满信心。</span></p>', null, '2', '如何获取优质的海外用户？如何制定针对性推广计划？如何实现流量最大程度的变现？让我们随大成网专访一探究竟。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('74', 'en_us', 'Fmarketing Interview: Effect proves strength', '          ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474274843.jpg\" style=\"width: 852px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Jason Cao, CEO of\nEptonic, was interviewed by Fmarketing on May 3rd, 2016 for the strategies of\noverseas advertising promotion, and he mainly shared these three important\nviews:</font></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">Firstly, “There is a great challenge for the mobile\ninternet market developing in China, but a great chance overseas.” Jason Cao\nsaid. He mentioned that globalization is the trend of future mobile internet\nand overseas market will be more standardized. It is obviously that the paying\nhabit of overseas users is far better than Chinese users’. <o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">Secondly, He said that “But meanwhile we are also\nfacing some challenges of entering the unfamiliar overseas markets.” He\nbelieved there were many challenges related to the product development,\noperation, and distribution, etc. For Eptonic, standardization and localization\nis the primary mission.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">Lastly, “Effect proves the strength” Jason Cao said,\n“Price, quality, effect, and service are significantly influencing customers’\nperceptions of enterprises.” Eptonic is committed to providing customers with\nthe overseas market analysis, including promotion strategies analysis of early\ntarget market. Jason Cao showed his strong determination of international\nexpansion.</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><o:p></o:p></font></span></p>', null, '1', 'Jason Cao, CEO of Eptonic, was interviewed by Fmarketing on May 3rd, 2016 for the strategies of overseas advertising promotion, and he mainly shared these three important views.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('79', 'en_us', 'Baijing Interview: Deciphering Eptonic-the pushing force of Swift Wifi', '   ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474525921.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">On March 16th, 2016, Jason Cao was\ninterviewed. <font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic was\nestablished in September 25th,2014, and with the rich experience of\nthe leaders, Eptonic was developed very quickly. “As one of the mobile internet\ncompanies in the country, I hope to develop a global brand.”, he said. It only\ntook more than one year to develop itself to become the leading promotion\nplatforms for apps and mobile games. Right now, it has hundreds of overseas\naffiliates, and advertising resources and good cooperation with some leading\nmedia, like Facebook and Google. Based on all of these advantages, Eptonic has\nhelped many domestic internet companies to achieve oversea success, taking\nSwift Wifi and Flash Keyboard as an example.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">He also shared Eptonic’s\nexpanding plan in 2016. “In the near future, we will integrate global traffic\nresources and enhance localization analysis to improve advertising performance\nand acquire high quality users.”, he said. Eptonic will keep on taking </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">South East Asia and North America markets as the main battlefield,\nanalyzing target markets and product characteristics more deeply and providing\ncustomers with the best advertising service.</span><br></p>', null, '1', 'On March 16th, 2016, Jason Cao was interviewed by Baijing for the reason why Eptonic can be so successful during such a short time.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('74', 'zh_cn', 'Fmarketing专访Eptonic曹远强：出海，要用实际效果说话', '       ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474274843.jpg\" style=\"width: 852px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">为了让对出海感兴趣的读者了解出海，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Fmarketing</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">将专门针对出海推出《海上风云》专题，专访一系列广告技术界出海的知名企业，为后面想做出海的企业做个借鉴。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">今天采访的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic CEO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">曹远强先生</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">国内已是红海，而国外却别有洞天</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">随着国内移动互联网红利的不断衰竭，出海已经由过去的“选修课”变成了“必修课”。在全球化趋势大潮下，面对市场规模更大、更成熟的海外市场，越来越多的中国移动互联网公司开始加入出海大潮，扬舟远航。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“国内移动互联网市场已经成为红海，很难再有发展空间，而国外却另一番天地。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic CEO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">曹远强表示，全球化是未来移动互联网的大趋势，与国内市场相比，海外市场更加规范有序，生态更完善，海外媒体相对更具有契约精神，沟通也更加直接高效，此外海外用户的付费习惯远超国内用户，出海大有可为。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成立于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月，而事实上，在这之前，曹远强已经在移动互联网出海领域深耕多年，积累了丰富的经验。公司刚成立，便签约了十几款产品准备在全球市场开始推广，并与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等建立了稳定的战略合作关系。凭借着其广阔的人脉和市场口碑，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">迅速走上快速发展轨道。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">经过几年的积累，如今</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">已经蜕变成国际领先的移动出海渠道商。目前，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">海外投放国家超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个，海外投放项目数百个，优质流量渠道数百家，每日超过百亿次展示，每月千万级海外安装，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">海外合作伙伴数百家，覆盖全球的移动网民。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>出海急需统一的行业规范</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">尽管当下移动出海大潮已然是势不可挡，但并不是每家公司都能赚得盆满钵满，相反失败的例子并不在少数。面对陌生的海外市场，不少企业踟蹰不前，徘徊在出海的大门之前。那么当下移动出海的痛点主要有哪些呢？</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">曹远强坦言，移动出海的痛点其实有很多，包括在产品研发、运营、发行等各个环节。单从推广上来看，市场不规范便是之一。面对出海热潮，众多公司纷纷涌入市场，造成鱼龙混杂。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“移动互联网的火热吸引越来越多互联网创业者，不过，市场喧嚣背后却呈现产业乱象。”曹远强表示，“乱象丛生的市场会使得像</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这样的移动互联网营销企业压力倍增，移动互联网出海推广是新兴产业，还没有形成统一的行业准则，只有建立起统一的行业规范，才能让行业更加公开、透明，推动行业的健康有序发展。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>用实际效果说话</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">面对出海的种种痛点，对于出海企业而言，选择一家靠谱的服务企业无疑是进行全球推广的不二选择。投入产出比无疑是众多企业最为在意的出海关键。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">便对症下药，从出海企业最为关心的“核心点”上入手，解决他们的困惑。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“价格、质量、效果是客户最关注的，同时也更加关注公司的服务。”曹远强表示，由于一些客户对市场并不了解，更倾向于由服务公司为他们提供全套解决方案。这也是当下不少公司主打所谓的“一站式整合营销服务”口号的主要原因。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“我们要用实际效果说话。”曹远强强调。前期，我们不仅为客户提供定向的海外市场分析，包括推广建议、支付建议、本地化建议等一系列的早期目标市场建议，还会为客户量身定制最优的整合营销解决方案。”</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">实践是最好的试金石。他透露，在正式推广前，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会对广告主的产品进行小量的测试，达到预期就按照计划投放，若未达预期效果，团队将调整投放方案，达成预期后再全量投放。这样严谨的投放流程，将极大程度地帮助广告主提高投放效果。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在曹远强看来，做生意要细水长流，而口碑便是其中的关键。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有很多长期合作的伙伴，而由他人推荐慕名而来找</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">合作的例子也不在少数。只有坚持服务品质，树立优良口碑，才会有更多的合作机会，实现企业的可持续发展。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年将是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的“品牌年”</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">曹远强告诉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Fmarketing</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，目前</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">主要有四大业务：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Eptonic Mediabuy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MDSP(Mobile Demand-side Platform </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">移动需求方平台</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMN(Eptonic\nMedia Network </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">广告交易私有平台</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和原生广告。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“我们最大的优势是我们的国际化专业推广团队”，他表示，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，从海外市场分析，到投放策略的定制，再到投放和结算，都有专业的团队实施。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对接了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">国际主流量广告平台，与全球各大媒体都有深度的合作，为广告主提供的不仅是获得最低价格展示和最优质流量的渠道服务，还有更多的增值服务和本地化定制服务。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">聊到技术时，曹远强觉得技术是服务的基础，说到底，最重要的是给广告主带来怎样的用户质量和价值。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“和同类公司相比，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的主要优势在于高质量的流量和专业的技术团队所带来的金牌服务和口碑，我们会利用我们的优势整合不同的媒体形式，为客户提供更加深入而全方位的服务，以使客户的海外推广达到最好的效果。”曹远强说。据悉，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">已助力百度、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APUS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">360Security</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Clean Master</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等众多知名品牌提供产品出海服务，并在海外市场的拓展方面取得显著成绩。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flash Keyboard</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Swift WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Power Clean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推广的三大明星产品。根据</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">App\nAnnie</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">统计，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">刚上线</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个月，就登顶</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">33</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家工具类应用榜，居</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">66</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家的工具类应用榜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TOP5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，拿下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">81</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家工具类应用榜前十名的好成绩；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flash Keyboard</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">更是高居</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Play</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">美国免费工具类应用排名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TOP4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">LionMobi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">公司旗下的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Power Clean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月推广至今，在海外获得惊人的成绩——</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">270</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿次曝光量、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿点击量、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">万的安装量，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月上旬，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Power Clean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">首获</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Play</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推荐，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月中旬，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Power Clean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">又连续斩获</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">次</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Play</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推荐。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">LionMobi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的合作还多次在包括</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">F8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在内的会议中被</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做为经典案例进行分享。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">曹远强透露，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年将是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的“品牌年”，公司将加大在品牌上的投入。“经过这些年的积累，我们已经到了厚积薄发的时刻。我们要走出去让更多的企业知道我们，我们也有信心能够助力更多的广告主出海，为其带来更高的投资回报率。”对于未来，曹远强充满了信心。</span></p>', null, '2', '为了让对出海感兴趣的读者了解出海，Fmarketing将专门针对出海推出《海上风云》专题，专访一系列广告技术界出海的知名企业，为后面想做出海的企业做个借鉴', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('75', 'en_us', 'GMIC 2016: We Were Here', '    2016-04-28 | Beijing, China', null, '<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474372847.jpg\" style=\"width: 994px;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Arial\">On April 28-30, 2016, GMIC was held in Beijing and\nEptonic attended this conference with the latest promotion strategies for apps\nand mobile games.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\">On April 28-30,\n2016, GMIC was held in Beijing. Taking “</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\">Mobile\nInfinity” as its theme, this conference attracted many mobile internet\ncompanies, e</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\">merging\nscience and technology innovation enterprises and developers in the world.\nEptonic attended this conference as expected.</span><br></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">At this\nconference, companies had tried various ways of bringing people with the latest\ninformation and achievement, such as through release conference for new\nproducts, speeches, booth display and so on.</span><br></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">As the global\nleader in mobile integrated marketing, Eptonic has long cooperation with\nFacebook, Google and many premium media resources. This time, Eptonic had sent\nout the most professional team to deal with customers’ questions relating to\noverseas promotion for apps and mobile games. And, customers spoke highly of\nEptonic.</span><br></p>', null, '1', 'From April 28th-30th, 2016, GMIC was held in Beijing and Eptonic attended this conference with the latest overseas promotion strategies for apps and mobile games.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('78', 'zh_cn', '《广告人》专访曹远强：用八年沉淀演绎后发制人', '  ', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474525571.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">在全球化趋势大潮下，越来越多的中国移动互联网公司开始加入出海大潮，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">就是其中一员。事实上，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">算是后入者，优势看上去并不那么明显，却出乎意料的成功，为此，《广告人》杂志对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic CEO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">曹远强进行了专访，就国内移动出海和企业的成功之路进行了深度解读。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当下移动出海已经成为一股热潮。面对国内已经厮杀成红海的市场，众多国内市场的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">开发者纷纷将目光瞄向海外，特别是手游和工具类产品，越来越重视海外市场的拓展，一方面是因为国内竞争的日益加剧，另一方面也是大家看到了海外市场巨大的增长空间。许多先行者已经在海外市场上获得了不小的成功，而在行业出海的大潮中，我们注意到了一个后发者迸发出的强大力量。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这家成立于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年年底，专注全球移动整合营销，服务跨屏广告和移动互联网广告推广的公司，却在成立后的一年时间里创造了年营收</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿人民币成绩，而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年的第一季度营收就已经做到了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">全年的水平。这样的后起之秀的夺目成绩，不免让人探究其背后成功秘诀。我们和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic CEO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">曹远强聊一聊</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">背后的故事。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>沉淀是为了更好的爆发</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">并没有赶上移动出海的先发优势，但是却深刻印证了厚积薄发之力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，曹远强进入互联网广告行业。大学时期的他曾以个人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Affiliate</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">进入互联网海外推广，他的合伙人何进也在那时一起进入这个行业。之后，工作室方式作为渠道角色全面进入海外推广。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010-2012</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，获得雅虎</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">RightMedia</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的全球一级代理权限。曹远强回忆起道：“当时熬更守夜的研究了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个月算法，通过自己的优化算法，使得发展非常迅速，并进一步开始了与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DoubleClick</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等全球性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">exchange</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的合作”，借助在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">exchange</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的技术经验积累，团队于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年全面做了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook Ads</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Adwords</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">精准推广项目，这些沉淀最终在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年底凝结成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。“之前，在互联网广告行业沉浸太多年了。”曹远强感慨道。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">旗下的四大平台</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic\nMediabuy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MDSP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Mobile Demand-side Platform</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">移动需求方平台）、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMN</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic\nMedia Network </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">广告交易私有平台）和原生广告体系。从买量角度来看，最核心的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Mediabuy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">业务，聚焦在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Adwords</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">带量能力。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">经过几年的积累，如今</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">已经蜕变成国际领先的移动出海渠道商。目前，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">海外投放国家超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个，海外投放项目数百个，优质流量渠道数百家，每日超过百亿次展示，每月千万级海外安装，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">海外合作伙伴数百家，覆盖全球的移动网民。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推广的三款明星产品，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flash\nKeyboard</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Power Clean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在海外的推广都获得了不错的成绩。比如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flash Keyboard </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月份在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Play</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">免费排行榜取得了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Top 4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的优秀成绩，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">也是超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">万的全球用户和两千万的分享</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">热点数。据第三方数据公司</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">App Annie</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">统计，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Swift WiFi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">刚上线</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个月，就登顶</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">33</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家工具类应用榜，进入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">66</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家的工具类应用榜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TOP5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，拿下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">81</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家工具类应用榜前十名的好成绩。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">LionMobi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">公司旗下的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Power Clean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月推广至今，在海外获得</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">270</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿次曝光量、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿点击量、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">万的安装量，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月上旬，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PowerClean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">首获</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Play</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推荐，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月中旬，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Power Clean</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">又连续斩获</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">次</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GooglePlay</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推荐。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">LionMobi</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的合作还多次在包括</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">F8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在内的会议中被</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做为经典案例进行分享。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><b>扬帆海外：红海之外的一片蓝海</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">随着移动互联网的不断发展，越来越多的创业公司进入该领域，激烈的竞争造就一片红海，曹远强则把目光放到了海外。“早期国内广告市场比较混乱，所以一直以来，我们没有涉足国内市场。海外市场必然越来越大，对于海外广告推广的需求也会越来越大。移动互联网是自带全球属性的。国内移动互联网市场已经成为红海，很难再有发展空间，而国外却另一番天地”曹远强说。针对海外市场的优势，曹远强认为体现在三个方面：首先，由于海外媒体相对更具有契约精神，沟通更加直接高效；其次，海外用户的付费习惯远超于国内用户，且一些国家的政策法规也更加完善；最后，世界范围内没有太多疯狂的搅局者。他总结道：“全球化是未来移动互联网的大趋势，与国内市场相比，海外市场更加规范有序，生态更完善，海外媒体相对更具有契约精神，沟通也更加直接高效，此外海外用户的付费习惯远超国内用户，出海大有可为。”</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">除了海外市场的秩序、效率等问题，曹远强也考虑到了中国企业是否适合出海的问题。他认为，在移动互联上，中国更多是走在了世界的前面，包括印度、巴西等市场要落后于中国市场的发展。因此，在海外分发上中国企业还很有竞争力。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">他补充道：“从区域市场分析，欧美市场和东南亚市场是中国产品出海的主战场，另外，针对不同的客户，一些发展中国家的市场也非常大，这些国家用户量很可观，且处于功能机向智能机的过渡过程，很多广告形式都有很好的表现，但这些国家的变现通道尚不明朗，因此目前很多急于变现的产品还没有大范围进入这种国家，但是一些工具应用类产品，以抢占用户市场为目的的公司，已经开始全面进入了。”</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">面对着新创公司在海外的纷纷布局，曹远强坦言，“移动互联网的火热吸引越来越多互联网创业者，不过，市场喧嚣背后却呈现产业乱象。移动出海的痛点其实有很多，包括在产品研发、运营、发行等各个环节。”曹远强表示，“乱象丛生的市场会使得像</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这样的移动互联网营销企业压力倍增，移动互联网出海推广是新兴产业，还没有形成统一的行业准则，只有建立起统一的行业规范，才能让行业更加公开、透明，推动行业的健康有序发展。”</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic2016</span><span style=\"font-family:\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">：打响品牌名片</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">传统营销领域，打响品牌名片非常重要。而在竞争愈发激烈移动互联领域，如何用一两个优势定义品牌也成为了重要因素。面对当前的竞争形势，曹远强并不彷徨，这份笃定来源于他对团队自信。</span>\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“我们最大的优势是我们的国际化专业推广团队”，他表示，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，从海外市场分析，到投放策略的定制，再到投放和结算，都有专业的团队实施。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对接了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">国际主流量广告平台，与全球各大媒体都有深度的合作，为广告主提供的不仅是获得最低价格展示和最优质流量的渠道服务，还有更多的增值服务和本地化定制服务。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">全球移动整合营销，服务可谓是重要因素，这也是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的另一大优势。“和同类公司相比，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的主要优势在于高质量的流量和专业的技术团队所带来的金牌服务和口碑，我们会利用我们的优势整合不同的媒体形式，为客户提供更加深入而全方位的服务，以使客户的海外推广达到最好的效果。”曹远强说。据悉，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">已助力百度、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APUS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">360Security</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Clean Master</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等众多知名品牌提供产品出海服务，并在海外市场的拓展方面取得显著成绩。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年将聚焦品牌塑造，加大在品牌上的投入。“经过这些年的积累，我们已经到了厚积薄发的时刻。我们要走出去让更多的企业知道我们，我们也有信心能够助力更多的广告主出海，为其带来更高的投资回报率。”曹远强笃定地说道。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一支丰富海外推广经验的团队，八年的沉淀积累，强大的技术优势，造就了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这一后起之秀，至此，我们不难推断出一年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿的营收业绩从何而来。未来，我们也有理由坚信，在曹远强与伙伴的带领下，这支在互联网行业摸爬滚打的团队将会在国内乃至全球移动广告领域，占据一席之地。</span><br></p>', null, '2', '事实上，在出海方面Eptonic算是后入者，优势看上去并不那么明显，却出乎意料的成功，对此CEO曹远强进行了深度解读。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('75', 'zh_cn', '在GMIC，我们用心感受移动世界的共振', '    2016-04-28 | 中国 · 北京', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474372847.jpg\" style=\"width: 994px;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GMIC2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（全球移动互联网大会）在北京国家会议中心拉开序幕，此次大会以“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Mobile Infinity</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（世界的共振）”为主题，吸引了来自全球的移动互联网领袖、新兴科技创新企业、顶尖开发者们汇聚首都，共同探讨移动互联网的发展。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为全球移动整合营销引领者，全新亮相本次大会。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">GMIC</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">全球移动互联网大会不仅是国内顶级企业讨论移动互联网行业最前沿的创新科技的舞台、更是全球顶尖企业领袖分享对移动互联网最新观点和看法的最前沿阵地。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">本届大会上，不少公司用新品发布、主题演讲和展台展示等方式带来了最新最近的产品。例如，作为大会顶级合作伙伴，华为荣耀已经第二次参加大会，并为观众带来了手机新品。而乐高集团旗下的乐高教育全新推出的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">WeDo 2.0</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将亮相未来峰会，这也是在华首次曝光。此外，易瞳科技也携全球首款</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MR</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">概念智能眼镜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">VMG</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在本次大会亮相。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为全球移动整合营销引领者，以全新的姿态亮相本次大会，一抹蔚蓝，为你展现清爽的科技视觉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><b>移动应用的全球化峰会</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日，在移动应用的全球化峰会的“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">App</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">全球化新兴趋势和未来机会”圆桌环节，白鲸社区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">魏方丹、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5MilesCEO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卢亮、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Musical.LY CEO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">阳陆育、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MicoCEO&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">张庆来、琥珀天气创始人汤城、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Yeecall CEO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">张磊对中国公司出海第二波浪潮的趋势和机会分享了很多干货经验。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果说，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年是中国公司出海第一波，那么以工具矩阵为主打的中国开发者的确享受到了很多红利，比如猎豹、名片全能王、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Camera360</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等等。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">而从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年底开始，工具红利逐渐被文化属性更强的社交、直播、内容等产品所盖过。无数个海外版映客、海外版今日头条、海外版陌陌爬上了东南亚、美国、欧洲的社交榜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Top10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。在这个第二波出海浪潮下，更加精细的本地化运营和文化理解，成为这些全球化</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">App</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的必做功课。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为全球移动整合营销推广平台，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">手握</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">国际流量资源以及遍布全球</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个国家的多样化海外媒体资源，国际化顶尖咨询团队，帮助来自世界各地的广告主更多元更精准的提供一站出海解决方案。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">来自世界各地的企业和开发者在展台对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提供的一站式出海的整合营销服务报以赞叹。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">随着“互联网</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">”、</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“大数据”、“移动互联网”的广泛传播，全球化潮流已成事实，产业环境不断优化，受众的消费能力也在提升。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将继续夯实在全球移动营销领域资源及技术优势，从行业宽度和行业深度两个方面进行战略拓展。一方面深度打造针对不同行业的企业出海垂直行业解决方案，一方面在将在多个行业领域进行全球布局。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">本届大会的召开不但跨界分析了移动互联网时代机遇与挑战，更为来自全球的创业者提供了见闻各行各业新思路的平台，连接世界，让创新实现价值，影响世界。</span></p><p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日，为期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">天的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GMIC</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">展会完美落幕，意犹未尽的小伙伴们不要落寞，挥一挥双臂，我们</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GMIC2017</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">再约！</span></p>', null, '2', '2016年4月28-30日，Eptonic亮相GMIC，备受瞩目。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('83', 'zh_cn', '「征•携手前行」CP对接沙龙圆满收官', '   2016-04-08 | 中国 · 重庆', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474527498.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日下午，爱游戏</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&amp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">西游汇主办的“征•携手前行”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">对接沙龙在重庆圆满落幕，本次活动聚集了众多来自成都、上海以及重庆本地的开发者。身为海外移动营销专家的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，作为重要嘉宾亮相了本次活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为出海营销专家，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的出场吸引了众多开发者的目光，在活动中为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">们深度解析了移动海外市场，并分享了出海实战经验。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">随着国内市场日趋白热化，开发者们也都在探寻新的市场以求突破，极具潜力的海外市场，就是新的增长突破口。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">各开发者纷纷表达了对海外市场浓厚的兴趣，也表示了对陌生市场环境的顾虑，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的实战推广经验，给了开发者极大的鼓励。本次活动中，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">为开发者特别提供了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个优质流量包，助其迈出出海的第一步。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">乘风而上，顺势而行。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span>将以领先的技术、专业的服务，携手开发者共征蓝海。</p>', null, '2', '身为海外移动营销专家的Eptonic，作为重要嘉宾亮相了本次活动。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('84', 'en_us', 'Eptonic attended the「G+Salon. Session of Fine Operation of Mobile Traffic」', '  2016-03-19 | Shenzhen, China', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474527851.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">On March 18, 2016, “G+Salon. Session of Fine Operation\nof Mobile Traffic” was held in Shenzhen with GMGC as the main sponsor and Eptonic,\nDataEye, OPPO and so on as the other sponsors, gathering many leading companies\nin the industry to share the opportunities and challenges.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Leo, VP in\nEptonic attended this salon and had a speech. He said there were many\nopportunities in foreign markets, but also there were problems of simple\ntraffic environment, different payment habit and property rights, cultural\ndifference and complicated overseas affiliates. Facing these problems, he\nshared his deep insights in the overseas promotion from the perspective of product\npreferences across the country, different markets characteristics and promotion\nstrategies.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n\n\n\n</p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Besides, he\nalso had deep discussion with the visiting guests for business model, science\nand technology and promotion experience, dedicating to help more domestic\nmobile internet companies to achieve overseas success.<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><o:p></o:p></font></span></p>', null, '1', 'On March 18th, 2016, “G+Salon. Session of Fine Operation of Mobile Traffic” was held in Shenzhen with GMGC as the main sponsor and Eptonic, DataEye, OPPO and so on as the other sponsors.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('84', 'zh_cn', 'Eptonic出席G+沙龙流量精细化运营专场，助力企业实现海外梦想！', '     2016-03-19 | 中国 · 深圳', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474527851.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GMGC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">全球移动游戏联盟联合</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataEye</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、爱思助手、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">OPPO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、泡椒互娱、中手游、正中集团等单位共同主办的“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">G+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">沙龙·移动流量精细化运营专场”活动于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日下午在深圳南山科兴科学园会议中心成功举办。众多优秀企业集聚一堂，探讨互联网市场的机遇和挑战，展开多领域的合作洽谈。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">此次受邀活动沙龙，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic VP </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">原家琪先生出席大会并发表精彩演讲，他指出在本土市场越来越饱和的状况下，出海也面临了单纯流量环境、付费习惯、产权问题、产品存在的文化差异以及海外渠道纷繁复杂等困境。因此如何突围困境，他从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在过往积累经验谈起，针对全球各地的产品偏好、不同地区的海外市场、出海策略的五个维度进行了精彩的分析。分享了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">长期与广告主合作的经验，以及各种挑战和拓展策略，并且为企业提供</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的整套效果营销解决方案，精彩内容引来在场众多互联网公司代表的关注！</span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n在现场，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic VP </span>原家琪先生与到访嘉宾进行商业模式探讨、技术交流、以及推广经验分享，希望助力更多互联网公司创造良好的海外条件，实现出海梦想！<br></p>', null, '2', 'Eptonic VP原家琪受邀出席沙龙，并发表精彩演讲。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('85', 'en_us', 'Eptonic Attended The Twelfth TFC Global Mobile Game Conference', '   2016-03-16 | Beijing, China', null, '<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">On March 17, 2016, the twelfth TFC global mobile game\nconference was held </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">at the Beijing\nInternational Convention Center and Eptonic attended it with the latest\ninformation and insights in overseas promotion strategies for apps and mobile\ngames.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">With “ New Beginning. New Opportunities. New\nBreakthroughs” as the theme, this conference gathered hundreds of enterprises\nin the field of mobile games and i</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ntelligent entertainment and so on. Besides, there\nwere thousands of new products, informing you the latest trend in this\nindustry.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">As the leading\nB2B mobile game conference, TFC had seen the germination, development, change\nand maturity of mobile game industry.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">This\nconference had integrated all the resources, covering the field of mobile\ngames, VR/AR, HTML5 game, hardware and so on.</span><br></p>', null, '1', 'On March 17th, 2016, the twelfth TFC global mobile game conference was held at the Beijing International Convention Center and Eptonic attended it.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('85', 'zh_cn', 'Eptonic强势出击第十二届TFC全球移动游戏大会', '    2016-03-16 | 中国 · 北京', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">由上方汇举办的国内移动游戏行业盛典“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第十二届</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TFC</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">全球移动游戏大会暨智能娱乐展”将于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16-18</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日在北京国际会议中心召开。</span><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">本次大会以“新起点·新机会·新突破”为主题，立足于移动游戏和智能娱乐全行业多个细分领域。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">强势出击，与来自全球</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">多个国家的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">余位重量级嘉宾、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">400</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">多家企业为移动游戏行业谋求新的发展机遇。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">现场将有超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">家优质</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，上千款产品展出。其中，周边主题会议及活动超</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">余场。预计将有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">多名业界精英与会，数百家知名媒体全程跟踪报道。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TFC2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">或带来超二十亿商机！</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B+C</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">”双向呈现。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为业内最具影响力的移动游戏</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B2B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">行业盛会，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TFC</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大会见证了整个移动游戏行业从萌芽、爆发、发展、变革到走向成熟的过程，成为行业最具前瞻性与公信力的品牌。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">本届<span lang=\"EN-US\">TFC</span>品牌全面升级，跨界整合“<span lang=\"EN-US\">B+C</span>”双端资源。<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>端展会将覆盖移动游戏、<span lang=\"EN-US\">VR/AR</span>、智能玩具和硬件、<span lang=\"EN-US\">HTML5</span>游戏、二次元产业、影视泛娱乐<span lang=\"EN-US\">IP</span>等多个领域，<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>端展会将专精二次元，利用国人自制、专业团队、优质原创的强大优势，打造“音影漫游”全景式互动体验。</p>', null, '2', '3月16-18日，Eptonic出击TFC全球移动游戏大会，携手全球伙伴谋求新的发展机遇', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('86', 'en_us', 'Eptonic Attended DOGAME Salon', ' 2016-03-07 | Beijing, China', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474529038.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">On March 7th, 2016 the salon mainly for CP was\nsuccessfully held with DOGAME and GMGC as the main sponsors, and Eptonic was\nproud to announce that it was invited to attend this salon. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">More than 300\ncompanies came to this activity, bringing audience the information and insights\ninto the product, affiliates, data and so on.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Global mobile\nInternet market continues to maintain rapid growth in 2016, especially in some\nemerging markets, like India, Indonesia, Vietnam, Brazil, South Africa, Thailand\nand so on and in the future, building global brand will be more and more\nenterprises’ target.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">As the global\nleading platform for overseas promotion of apps and mobile games, Eptonic\nbrought audience the latest information about the creative advertising forms\nand strategies, helping domestic companies to achieve overseas success.</span><br></p>', null, '1', 'On March 7th, 2016 the salon activity of CP was successfully held with DOGAME and GMGC as the main sponsors, and Eptonic was proud to announce that it was invited to attend this salon.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('86', 'zh_cn', 'Eptonic & DOGAME CP路演活动圆满收官', '   2016-03-07 | 中国 · 北京', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"upload/article/uid_45_1474529038.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GMGC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">大会前期由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Dogame</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">游戏兵工厂、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GMGC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">主办，和创</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4S</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">游戏、游戏观察协办的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">路演沙龙活动圆满收官，作为赞助商及重要嘉宾的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">隆重亮相本次活动，与众多优秀公司带来一场干货十足的分享会，现场气氛热烈、互动不断。大家对各位嘉宾真切而精彩的演讲一致点赞！据</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DOGAME</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">官方了解，从产品到渠道平台、数据等各个方面，到场人数为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">多人，为更好的了解团队、产品以及合作机会，不少</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">团队、投资、运营发行以及媒体的朋友参与了活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年全球移动互联网市场依然保持告诉增长，尤其是像印度、印尼、越南、巴西、南非、泰国等智能手机正在加速普及的新兴市场，逐渐成为全球关注的新宠儿，是各企业不可忽视的移动营销新战场。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年，全球移动互联网的“残酷杀戮”更加惨烈，而“全球化”将成为移动互联网企业迈向未来发展壮大的必经之路。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">此次参加本次活动，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span>不仅展示了其在广告创新形式、投放质量控制、<span lang=\"EN-US\">MDSP</span>定向投放以及<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mediabuy</span>投放优化等技术成果，也是<span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic2016</span>年首次全新亮相。</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span>作为海外推广移动营销服务商，对品牌普及及用户获取有着独特的渠道资源与推广理念，本次参会演讲及多方同行展开了探讨沟通，相信对整个行业的发展进步都会产生积极作用。</p>', null, '2', 'Eptonic商务总监姚志参加路演并发表精彩演讲，为开发者深度解读出海发展之路。', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('87', 'en_us', 'Eptonic attended ASW2016, seeing the globalization of mobile advertising', '2111111', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/http://www.eptonic.biz/sites/upload/article/uid_45_1474529471.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">As the world\'s largest internet marketing summit, Affiliate\nSummit West 2016 was held from January 10th to 12th in America, gathering many\ninternet operators and advertising platforms. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">As the global\nleading platform of overseas promotion for apps and mobile games, Eptonic\nattended this conference and brought people with the latest information and\ninsights into the advertising trend in 2016.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Mobile\nadvertising had achieved explosive growth in 2015, due to the development of\ntechnology, and mobile device. According to research, the global mobile\nInternet spending amounted to $68.69 billion in 2015 and it would amount to $100\nbillion in 2016.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic\nachieved a lot at this conference and in the future, it will keep on moving\nforward and becoming the top one platform for domestic companies to promote\noverseas.<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><o:p></o:p></font></span></p>', null, '1', 'As the world\'s largest internet marketing summit, Affiliate Summit West 2016 was held from January 10th to 12th in America, gathering many internet operators and advertising platforms.', null);
INSERT INTO `ed_article_i18n` VALUES ('87', 'zh_cn', 'Eptonic参展ASW大会，见证2016移动广告全球化进程177777', ' 12222222222222', null, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; \">投入人员<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">日，全球最大规模的互联网营销峰会的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Affiliate Summit West 2016(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">简称</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ASW)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">在美国拉斯维加斯拉开帷幕。本次峰会云集了来自全球各地的互联网运营商、平台商等行业巨头，分享创新的产品与思路，交流行业的发展趋势。作为国内移动变现出海的佼佼者，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">组队出征此次峰会，由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">曹远强先生带领这支精英团队出现在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Vegas</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">会场，与行业精英探讨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年及未来移动广告营销的发展趋势，寻求更广阔的合作空间。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">移动广告在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年取得了爆发性的增长。技术的迅猛发展、移动设备的普及和移动基础设施的完善使得移动广告投放成为市场营销战略中一个不容忽视的环节。据研究，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年全球移动互联网支出达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">$686.9</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿，较</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">61.1%</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的涨幅，并将在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年达到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">$1000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亿以上，占据数字市场的大半江山。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ASW</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会议官方数据）</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为全球领先的媒体精准投放平台，应用国际先进定向技术，打造“精准营销”独特市场理念，真正实现对目标受众的精准传播，助力国内企业进军海外市场，达到最大程度商业利益。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span>作为国内专注于提供企业产品出海服务的推广平台，此次远赴拉斯维加斯参展收获满满。<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span>年，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Eptonic</span>会站在全球高度，在产品、技术、大数据及服务等方面不断发力创新，建立一个“更高效”的移动营销世界，成为企业“一站出海”的重要桥梁。</p>', null, '2', 'Eptonic赴美参加Affiliate大会，与全球站长共商移动广告全球化进程。', null);
